{"tid":814462,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇Ling U 劉智鵬既料爆下？","createTime":"2018-09-11T09:09:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-11T12:43:55.000Z","uid":167928,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"b936a13d97d247fd68b9c61963b62a87d34e4058","tid":814462,"uid":167928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T09:09:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">本身是嶺大香港與華南歷史研究部主任、曾為古諮會及城規會成員的劉智鵬</span></span>，曾認為07年被拆卸的皇后碼頭無重大歷史價值。而他4年前受粉嶺高爾夫球場委託，就球場歷史進行研究，更曾指清拆高球場是「走保育回頭路」。今早他出席商台節目時否認雙重標準，認為香港高球場是殖民地首個或第2個現代康樂設施，故值得保留。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180911/58668051\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180911%2F58668051&d=zprXbIA%2Fr9l9%2BaN0GqaKwjA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=3aa85109\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180911%2F58668051&h=130bf398\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180911/58668051</a>"},{"pid":"4fb1e8feb7f1073d7f28261c340ed138417f4b81","tid":814462,"uid":167928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T09:09:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d33a3cc966c1372bfc9a299ba0b84e2b687b1a6","tid":814462,"uid":167928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T09:10:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a41379c8732909e477bff64e49c6